{"tid":1894483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［世界末日］南韓單日再增 161 宗 累計 763 宗確診　11 軍官受感染 意大利破150宗","createTime":"2020-02-24T03:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T04:28:35.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"074c1ed7c8e4b1af01f4db0ddd642b6d6b4187fe","tid":1894483,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續於韓國爆發。根據韓聯社報道，截至今日（24日）早上9時，累計確診增至 763宗，較昨日新增161宗，當中129宗個案與新天地大邱教會有關。至於死亡病例則新增1宗至7宗，死者為62歲男子，與前日死亡的第6宗病例同樣來自慶尚北道的清道大南醫院。<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓《韓聯社》報道，已有11名軍人確診，其中陸軍有8例確診，海軍、空軍和海軍陸戰隊各有1例。軍方表示，新增的4名軍人疑似和軍營內的患者接觸後感染了病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E5%A2%9E-161-%E5%AE%97-%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88-763-%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-11-%E8%BB%8D%E5%AE%98%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25A2%259E-161-%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588-763-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-11-%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%2F&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=6628126d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25A2%259E-161-%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588-763-%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-11-%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%2F&h=20d9a514\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E5%A2%9E-161-%E5%AE%97-%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88-763-%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-11-%E8%BB%8D%E5%AE%98%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93/</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情蔓延全球各地之際，意大利一名罹患癌症年長女性因為感染武漢肺炎不治，成為境內第3宗死亡病例。同時意大利全國確診病例數錄得 152 宗，成為武漢肺炎疫情最嚴重的歐洲國家。威尼斯嘉年華最後兩天的活動同樣因疫情取消。由於意大利政府昨天下令封鎖境內11座城鎮，當地超市出現搶購潮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E7%A0%B4-150-%E5%AE%97-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88-3-%E6%AD%BB-%E5%A5%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E6%9B%BE%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BE%86%E5%BE%80%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%25A0%25B4-150-%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588-3-%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25BE%2580%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25BB%258A%2F&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=6218e92b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%25A0%25B4-150-%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E8%25A8%2588-3-%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25BE%2580%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25BB%258A%2F&h=65fc9a57\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E7%A0%B4-150-%E5%AE%97-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88-3-%E6%AD%BB-%E5%A5%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E6%9B%BE%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BE%86%E5%BE%80%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A/</a>"},{"pid":"5670d2d38795f7e93237526bfee81b058a